**Additional Protections**:
- **Time-limited cross-tenant grants**: All support access expires after configurable period (default 4 hours)
- **Scope-limited access**: Cross-tenant grants specify exact permissions (READ_INVOICES, VIEW_USERS, etc.)
- **Comprehensive audit trail**: All cross-tenant access logged with full context for compliance
- **Anomaly detection**: Alert when user accesses unusual number of different tenants
- **Grant approval workflow**: Cross-tenant access requires approval from target tenant admin
- **Regular grant review**: Automated job revokes unused grants after 30 days of inactivity

Multi-tenant data isolation is critical for SaaS applications. A common vulnerability occurs when tenant boundaries are not enforced at every data access point, leading to cross-tenant data leakage.

**VULNERABLE CODE**:

```go
